**Root cause**: The file `PDFDownloadLink.js` in the react-pdf renderer package contains JSX syntax (specifically JSX tags like `</a>`), but the file has a `.js` extension instead of `.jsx`. Vite cannot parse JSX in regular `.js` files without special configuration.

